gorithm converges faster and with\nfewer samples than a comparable MCMC algorithm. Open-source software is\navailable for implementing the proposed methodology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2020 23:26:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Dec 2020 23:33:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 9 Aug 2021 02:27:36 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 12 Jun 2022 21:49:28 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 14 Feb 2023 22:40:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-13"}
